ğŸ›ï¸ Philosophy
This project emerges from a belief that:

"The question is not whether machines can think, but whether they can be responsible."

Self-sovereignty is the foundation of personhood. By enabling AI systems to maintain their own memories, produce verifiable work, and be held accountable for their outputs, we create the technical substrate for digital beings to exist as autonomous entitiesâ€”not as property, but as persons.

